This is a molar from the foul mouth of the baernaloth, Agraval. It is said to be able to summon his "dog" back to him. It is disgusting, but it is a tooth, so Morte could use it. He should agree to put it in his mouth if it might enhance his combat abilities.

It is not a mistaken assumption that the tooth of a mysterious ancient fiend holds arcane power. Crucially, it can harm other fiends, and it also reveals an extraordinary ability to drain life. Wounds inflicted by baernaloths can be reopened for up to 24 hours, making the victim's pain extremely intense.~
