This holy weapon was forged from the pure iron of Mt. Celestia by the Anunnaki fire god, Girru, in the Forge of Undying Flame, his divine realm in Mercuria. Girru's domains also include justice and law, making him a fitting creator for this ritual tool designed to cleanse the world of evil. Ancient magic and incantations, called nam-búr-bi, are engraved on the sword. They are meant not only to ward off evil but also, as they literally state, to "bolster the king's self-confidence, strengthen his resolution, and steel his will to fight." In practice, this translates to increased Charisma, Wisdom, Armor Class, and fearlessness.~
