Long ago, it was worn by Innaya, queen of the devas who ruled from the city of Iadmon in Amoria, Elysium. One day, however, the city was uprooted from its foundations by the dragon god Task, who transported it to the Lower Planes and placed it on the surface of Gehenna, covering the entrance to a dragon lair, his divine realm. Innaya perished along with most of Iadmon's inhabitants, and Task plundered nearly all of its treasures, leaving only a handful, among which this earring was included. The earring retained a fragment of Innaya's wondrous aura, even when lost between the planes as it fell from her ear.~
