These bolts contain the power of a primordial elemental fire deity, the Lord of Flames Kossuth. His divine realm is the Crimson Pillar in the Elemental Plane of Fire. It is a globe of flame ten miles wide and so unimaginably hot that the rest of the plane seems almost chilly.

That is where these missiles draw their power from. Even the smallest fraction of this power can wreak havoc on your enemies.~
@500191 = ~Bolts of Vengeful Storms~
@500192 = ~BOLTS OF VENGEFUL STORMS
Damage: 2-5 (crushing)
Enchantment: +3
