The voices for the original Planescape: Torment were recorded over two decades ago. Blizzard in Baator features unused lines recorded by the original actors from that time. We would like to dedicate this mod to the actors who brought the voices of the game's unique characters to life in both language versions and who are no longer with us.

Tony Jay (1933-2006)
